      "timestamp": "2026-06-04T08:12:32.575+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "No. CMOS standard cells have NAND2 and AOI amd OAI cells that don't have inverter at the end and these cells will be used quite a lot in the synthesized netlist.",
